uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model

Interface DObject

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DObjectShell

    public interface DObject
    Interface implemented by all classes in the Object Model (OM). Each such class will be bound to a CFrame object, representing a concept-level frame in the Frames Model (FM), and individual instantiations of the class will be bound to IFrame objects, representing specific "instantiations" of the concept-level frame.

    All fields on implementing classes that are part of the OM will be represented by DField objects of various kinds. At the class-level such fields are bound to specific CSlot objects, whilst at the object-level they will be bound to corresponding ISlot objects.
